item.title: RHCSA Community Study Guide
item.description: A community study guide for anyone that wants to study for the RHCSA exam. The idea is that anyone preparing for the exam can use the information here, as well as contribute (add, update, correct) to make it better. The aim is to have a free and Open Source study guide that is always up to date and with the best content.
